{"tid":2176457,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"充電唔煩 | 實試香港首個Tesla V3超級充電站 叉滿64%只需28分鐘快過食餐飯","createTime":"2020-08-27T05:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T06:40:42.000Z","uid":323911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"27ac58c8bffd112bc54dc0c4d79b2049dc8a0671","tid":2176457,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"常言道電動車最麻煩就是充電要等，不過作為電動車的翹楚，Tesla在發展更先進的充電技術可謂不遺餘力，近日他們就正式在將軍澳The LOHAS推出全港首個V3超級充電站。<br />\n<br />\n若果大家有試用過Tesla的超級充電站都會知道其充電速度已是冠絕全港，一般充電也不消一小時。不過Tesla就標榜V3超級充電站可以將原來的119kW的充電峯值提升至250kW，效能足足高出一倍之多。理論上在這種充電功率下，一部Model 3 Long Range其實只需5分鐘即可補充約120公里的續航里程。<br />\n<br />\n聽見這個新充電站如此厲害，CarMan就決定實試一下這套V3超級充電站看看實際的充電功率有否這麼驚人。以今次測試為例，我們就特意安排了一部Long Range版Model 3作為我們的「白老鼠」。在充電之前，這部Model 3的電量只剩下16%，當我把充電線插進充電口的時候，Model 3的屏幕上所顯示的充電功率已迅速提升至200kW的水平左右，電量也不消5分鐘已增加至30%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DDfylltjLEGX5oYTiV2zAytCX4E=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XIJCZIJUBVES7P3ESIKX36GM4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDDfylltjLEGX5oYTiV2zAytCX4E%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXIJCZIJUBVES7P3ESIKX36GM4U.jpg&h=c5f14cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCarMan就決定實試一下這套V3超級充電站看看實際的充電功率是否這麼驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o_Oa-c8SnIdyv7iXqz_l0kB3Nrg=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IKZAZZKKGVHPRGVRDH4AB5G7FM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo_Oa-c8SnIdyv7iXqz_l0kB3Nrg%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIKZAZZKKGVHPRGVRDH4AB5G7FM.jpg&h=a7f66261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在充電之前，這部Model 3的電量只剩下16%，當採用V3超級充電站的時候電量也不消5分鐘已增加至30%。<br />\n<br />\n雖然實測功率未及官方聲稱的250kW，不過實際的功率輸出還是要視乎充電站電力供應的狀況。除了電力供應這個因素之外，車輛本身的電池溫度亦是一項限制功率的主要因素，事關電池在充電途中也會慢慢升溫，因此為了確保電池的安全和健康，充電站也會因應當刻的電池溫度來調節輸出功率。這也解釋了為何充電過程去到中段的時候，充電功率也下降至119kW左右，而當電量接近80%的時候，輸出功率更慢慢下降50至60kW水平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y1FlyieK9I2vjzhb3Kou0Lj1MCQ=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYAOO56QWJFGLONEL24HLTXPRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY1FlyieK9I2vjzhb3Kou0Lj1MCQ%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYAOO56QWJFGLONEL24HLTXPRA.jpg&h=2497bfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然實測功率未及官方聲稱的250kW，不過實際的功率輸出還是要視乎充電站電力供應的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n儘管今次實測的數據並沒有官方所聲稱的那麼誇張，但V3超級充電站的充電速度亦是香港前所未見的高，以今次這部Model 3為例，從16%電量充至80%也只需28分鐘。這個時間隨時比你吃一頓午餐還要快，再加上V3超級充電站的價錢仍然維持在以往Tesla超級充電站每度電$3.1的水平，試問這樣兩全其美的方案又叫人怎能抗拒呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lXNLivKIZhV_eMUOwaRKYv-HfsQ=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R65SNJJFPFGLJILXL7THGL6OJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlXNLivKIZhV_eMUOwaRKYv-HfsQ%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR65SNJJFPFGLJILXL7THGL6OJE.jpg&h=3f3934be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以今次這部Model 3為例，從16%電量充至80%也只需28分鐘，這個時間隨時比你吃一頓午餐還要快。<br />\n<br />\n說到這裏一眾Tesla Model S和Model X的車主就可能會好奇他們的充電速度會否有異呢？事實上Model S和Model X都是相對較舊的Tesla型號，因此充電口亦跟Model 3有所不同。若果2019年5月1日前製造的Model S和Model X車主想用V3超級充電站的話，就須要向廠方購買一個CCS Combo 2轉插器（售價$1,250），那麼就可以最高150kW的功率充電（軟件更新後可高達225kW）。至於在2019年5月1日前製造的Model S和Model X則須回到Tesla維修中心進行充電口改裝（$2,250，費用包括一個CCS Combo 2轉接器）。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，位於The LOHAS的充電站只是Tesla在香港擴大V3超級充電站版圖的第一步，廠方將於未來數月在港島南區、中區、九龍西增設更多V3 Supercharging超級充電站。相信隨着這類配套日漸成熟，選用電動車的人只會越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rzWUMrnFjmDLzfHeCrzu1ZwvKdQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MWLFLP4J5GQTJFB5WXGSM532I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrzWUMrnFjmDLzfHeCrzu1ZwvKdQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MWLFLP4J5GQTJFB5WXGSM532I.jpg&h=f8731f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe LOHAS充電站只是Tesla在香港擴大V3超級充電站版圖的第一步，廠方將於未來數月在港島南區、中區、九龍西增設更多V3 Supercharging 超級充電站。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：梁彥韜<br />\n<br />\n攝影：李卓霖"},{"pid":"28a9f7c97727048c068bbd64def7d365815a784a","tid":2176457,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"問題係香港人食餐飯唔洗28 分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bb6b26170ad1385539de516cd07f2564557e42","tid":2176457,"uid":55445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"28a9f7c97727048c068bbd64def7d365815a784a","tid":2176457,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"問題係香港人食餐飯唔洗28 分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"問題係十幾架車等緊位充<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550e710ea5c899434a222cfba59a1bc022ad874d","tid":2176457,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"發財都要立品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿高追TSLA泡沫"},{"pid":"07e92a556428d661e35c50665340f94a0f9af05c","tid":2176457,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550e710ea5c899434a222cfba59a1bc022ad874d","tid":2176457,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"發財都要立品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿高追TSLA泡沫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"binc 